THE VISION
This is not just a game. This is a spiritual tool disguised as entertainment.
Players will:
Learn to recognize manipulation in real life
Practice setting boundaries
Develop compassion for the wounded
Understand that discernment is a skill, not a gift
Experience the truth that "not all spirits are evil — some are just wounded"
And they will do all of this while having fun, laughing at the absurdity, and
sharing their experiences with friends.
The Spiritual Planes is:
A game for people who think
A social experience for people who feel
A spiritual journey for people who wonder
And a damn good time for everyone else
